{"tid":2005250,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"NASA 與湯告魯斯合作   新電影將在國際太空站實地取景拍攝","createTime":"2020-05-07T03:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T05:08:05.000Z","uid":105567,"like":54,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"56e56119f188c37e792de89a5e08036989b4ee73","tid":2005250,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:51:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/05/07/tom-cruise-movie-in-space/movie-2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F05%2F07%2Ftom-cruise-movie-in-space%2Fmovie-2%2F&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdYHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=89c7f293\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/05/07/tom-cruise-movie-in-space/movie-2/</a><br />\n<br />\n為了減低太空計劃的成本開支，自從 Jim Bridenstine 在 2018 年接任美國太空總署（NASA）的署長後，不斷透過將太空項目商業化。Bridenstine 的搵錢大計包括為太空船尋求商業冠名贊助，甚至讓普通人有機會登上他們位於太空的設施。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這名想法多多的署長日前透露，NASA 正在和著名影星 Tom Cruise 合作，他的下一部電影將會在國際太空站取景拍攝。這將會是首部真正在太空拍攝的電影，Bridenstine 未有透露有關電影的相關細節，但早前流出的消息指電影並非屬於《職業特工隊》系列。<br />\n<br />\n報導此消息的網站 Deadline 提到，Elon Musk 創辦的太空探索公司 SpaceX 亦會參與其中，可能會為拍攝的人員提供往返地面和國際太空站的飛行服務。消息指電影還在初期籌備階段，還未有電影公司參與其中，亦未知上映日期，不過 SpaceX 的 Crew Dragon 太空船載人服務最快要到 2021 年下半年才有望推出。透過 Tom Cruise 電影的知名度吸引更多企業，NASA 有望將國際太空站商業化。"},{"pid":"fb940fb176c2d30f86a28e612a266adeb9c903e7","tid":2005250,"uid":61954,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:05:43.000Z","msg":"拍戲拍到上太空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f3d2c66a1fe80c4e3a4c1c2cd0fbd2f4bf50f5","tid":2005250,"uid":19712,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:06:55.000Z","msg":"準備揸穿梭機"},{"pid":"15bcd1a341c14ba5a0aca5571f17ef2cc6d2c346","tid":2005250,"uid":149122,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:07:10.000Z","msg"